# Release Design Decision for tag 0.0.2

# Objectives
- Enhance the CLI application to support coding agent functionalities

# Key Decisions
- Enable streaming responses from Gemini models for real-time feedback
    - Use a trick to avoid flickering during streaming by measuring terminal height and adjusting rendering accordingly
- Implement input history navigation using arrow keys for improved user experience
- Store and load input history from a file to maintain state across sessions